"{\"uid\": \"tribune.com.pk-story-2487217-biologist-richard-dawkins-says-his-comments-on-imane-khelif-caused-facebook-to-remove-his-account\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"IE  Dawkins claimed he was censored due to his remarks on Algerian boxer Imane Khelif's Olympic eligibility.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 108, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 66, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.93529874910971, \"rank\": 0.048407558496243196, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 73, \"end\": 85, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"British biologist and author Richard Dawkins announced on August 10 that his Facebook account had been deleted, a move he claims was due to his comments regarding Algerian boxer Imane Khelif's participation in the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 110, \"to\": 344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 110, \"end\": 117, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9976132482512814, \"rank\": 0.0013077995358300762, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 139, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Dawkins\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Richard Dawkins\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Dawkins\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Richard_Dawkins\"}, {\"begin\": 273, \"end\": 281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.93529874910971, \"rank\": 0.048407558496243196, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 288, \"end\": 300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421623295, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The incident has sparked a broader debate on social media about freedom of speech and censorship.\", \"from\": 346, \"to\": 443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dawkins, known for his outspoken views, took to X (formerly Twitter) to voice his concerns about the deletion of his Facebook account.\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 579, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He tweeted, \\\"My entire @facebook account has been deleted, seemingly (no reason given) because I tweeted that genetically male boxers such as Imane Khalif (XY undisputed) should not fight women in Olympics.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course my opinion is open to civilised argument.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 839, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But outright censorship?\\\"\", \"from\": 840, \"to\": 865, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversy revolves around Khelif, who has become a subject of debate following her qualification for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 867, \"to\": 987, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dawkins previously expressed his views on the matter in a tweet on July 29, where he stated, \\\"Two men, pretending to be women, are being allowed to compete against real women in the Olympics,\\\" which was interpreted as a reference to the inclusion of transgender athletes in the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 1287, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The deletion of Dawkins' Facebook account has ignited discussions about the boundaries of free speech on social media platforms, particularly when addressing sensitive issues related to gender and sports.\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"COMMENTS  Comments are moderated and generally will be posted if they are on-topic and not abusive.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For more information, please see ourComments FAQ  This material may not be published, broadcast, rewritten,                     redistributed or derived from.\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1754, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Unless otherwise stated, all content is                     copyrighted \\u00a9 2025 The Express Tribune.\", \"from\": 1755, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": []}]}"